  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook, stirring occasionally, until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook, stirring constantly, for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, and cayenne pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the split peas, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, until the peas are tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the fresh parsley and cilantro.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed."
